                            [Mini Mini NT]                            
                                                                        
                                                                      
                                                                        
     In this episode Mark Surprises school teacher Steve Walton from     
     Haywards Bay in NSW with a trip to the Northern Territory. The     
    guys hooked up with Cannon charters and fish the Mini Mini river     
     system in search of the mighty Barramundi. Fishing in untouched     
   creeks they do battle with some incredible fish as Steve lands his    
   first ever Barra and chases the $5000 challenge. Mark also tangles    
     with a saltwater crocodile that needed some delicate handling.
